List creators can add or remove columns in Actionable List Members to view relevant information. The default Record Status filter shows only active records. You can create bulk action configurations with OmniScripts and assign tasks to colleagues.

Add or Remove Columns in Actionable List Members to View Relevant Information
List creators can customize the table in Actionable List Members to suit their needs.
Improve the Efficiency of List Creators with the Record Status Filter
With the new default filter, list creators can focus on active records without applying the filter each time.
Streamline the List Creator Workflow with Contextual OmniScripts on Bulk Action Panel
List creators can improve productivity by including OmniScripts in bulk action configurations.
Save Time and Improve Efficiency with Bulk Action Plans
List creators can generate action plans in bulk for selected actionable list members.
